  }
}

###

### Cancel Existing Order
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/orders/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "orderId": 1
}

###

### Get Order Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/orders/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

