### ============================================
### NOTES
### ============================================
### 
### 1. Replace {{token}} with your actual JWT token
###    Token should be obtained from the authentication endpoint
###
### 2. BaseUrl is set to https://localhost:5001
###    Change according to your environment
###
### 3. API Version: v1
###    Can be specified in URL or via x-api-version header
###
### 4. All endpoints require:
###    - Valid JWT token in Authorization header
###    - Application/JSON content type
###
### 5. Rate Limiting:
###    - 100 requests per 60 seconds per user/IP
###    - Returns 429 Too Many Requests when exceeded
###
### 6. Validation Rules:
###    - Card Number: 13-19 digits
###    - Expiration: MM/YY format
###    - CVC: 3-4 digits
###    - ZipCode: 5 digits or 5+4 format
###
### 7. Health Checks:
###    - /health: General API health
###    - /health/ready: Includes database connectivity check
###
